 Silverlight got a life support by Microsoft up to 2021 ", "[18]", "!"), mdx("p", null, "TypeScript is used by huge projects, and not only from Microsoft. Here is a quick list of companies using TypeScript."), mdx("ul", null, mdx("li", {
